BookmyShow  Requirements

Actor
    App User
    Theater partner
    System


App User
     - Search based on Movies/Events or Theater Name
     - Select movies and Theatre
     - Rating and Votes for the all movies
     - Select language or 2d/3d/Imax
     - Filter Movie based on price / show timings and date 
     - select number of seats
     -  Seat availability
     - Payment 

 Theater partner
     -  movie availabilty
     -  scan the ticket to check  if it is valid or not
     -  cancel/ reschedule / update movie
     -  

System
     - login
     - notification -  Remainders
     - send ticket to email /message
     - offers
     -  multiple users book at same time (concurrent Bookings)  *** 
